---

# Current Status

Cortex is currently under active development.

The first milestone is a production-ready prototype for Danish General Practice.

Initial focus areas include:

- Musculoskeletal complaints
- Acute symptoms
- Chronic disease management

---

# Design Philosophy

Technology should never become the focus of the consultation.

The patient should.

Every feature should make the consultation calmer, simpler and more clinically focused.

